direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **strategy-scope-review**

  - &lt;RHAISTRAT-NNNN&gt; or all
  - context: fork · model opus
  - invoked by /strategy-review
  - tools: Read, Grep, Glob
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Mode (decision) ---

mode: |md
  **Mode?**

  - local/strat-tasks present?
  - else artifacts/ (CI)
| {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Cross-reference ---

xref: |md
  **Cross-ref RFE + prior reviews**

  - read strategies (strat-tasks)
  - RFE originals (strat-originals)
  - prior reviews &rarr; re-review?
  - deliverables vs RFE criteria
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Assess scope (LLM) ---

assess: |md
  **Assess scope** (PO lens)

  - right-sized? (feature, not 3+ / not a task)
  - effort matches scope? (M vs L/XL)
  - bounded? in / out-of-scope explicit
  - complete capability delivered?
  - silently expands / shrinks RFE?
  - requirements prioritized (P0/P1/P2)?
  - flag scope traps ("full support for")
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Structured verdict ---

output-verdict: |md
  **Structured verdict** (per strategy)

  - Scope assessment
  - Effort vs scope
  - RFE coverage
  - Scope risks
  - Recommendation
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Flow ---

entry -> mode
mode -> xref: "local"
mode -> xref: "artifacts (CI)"
xref -> assess
assess -> output-verdict
